00:28:28,673 --> 00:28:30,197
and messed up.

336
00:28:31,009 --> 00:28:34,035
So if you're hanging in,

337
00:28:34,979 --> 00:28:38,471
waiting for me to metamorphose
into the woman you want,

338
00:28:38,983 --> 00:28:42,817
