and Harris is not in love with me.

472
00:40:20,885 --> 00:40:22,375
Are you sure?

473
00:40:23,387 --> 00:40:24,479
Yes.

474
00:40:25,790 --> 00:40:27,690
Do you want to know how I know?

475
00:40:28,225 --> 00:40:29,419
Yeah.

476
00:40:30,795 --> 00:40:32,524
Because I asked him.

477
00:40:32,596 --> 00:40:33,927
